      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly with a persistent smoke issue, and the transmission slips when shifting between gears. The body shows heavy rust along the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior has significant tearing and a non-functional electrical system. It is best suited as a parts car or a total restoration project for a dedicated hobbyist.",
